    <h2>Conclusion</h2>
    <p>This analysis highlighted both successes and areas for growth in my weekly activity. Key next steps include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Increasing daily consistency (focus on workdays).</li>
        <li>Participating in more group activities to stay motivated.</li>
    </ul>

